  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>As Technician you will be responsible to:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide service and repair for custom made earpieces, (In-The-Ear) ITE and (Behind-The Ear) BTE hearing instruments</li><li>Handle urgent custom-made earpiece orders</li><li>Quality check and testing of all outgoing hearing instruments</li><li>Complete the necessary documents after packing all outgoing instruments</li><li>Provide support in logistics when necessary</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties assigned by the supervisor</li></ul><p><strong>We are looking for an individual with:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum N / O Level / NITE/ ITE in Electrical or Electronics</li><li>Able to work under pressure with minimal supervision</li><li>Focused, quick learner, strategically prioritizes work, committed</li><li>Able to communicate effectively across functions</li><li>Basic knowledge in IT (Microsoft office)</li><li>Soldering skill is preferable</li><li>Fresh graduates without relevant experiences but are keen to learn about hearing instruments technology can also apply</li></ul>",
